                "text": "A living creature injured by a botfly swarm\u2019s attack must make a DC 14 Fortitude save or be infested with the swarm\u2019s larvae. The larvae may be cut out of the host with a DC 15 Heal check, though each attempt inflicts 1d8 points of damage whether or not it\u2019s successful. A cure disease spell destroys all larvae without further harm to the host.<br/><br/><i>Botfly larvae</i>: infestation; <i>save</i> Fort DC 14; <i>onset</i> 1 day; <i>frequency</i> 1/day; <i>effect</i> 1d4 Con damage."
